data.description: Absolutely stunning ranch in a quiet neighborhood. This house has it all! Close to amenities and highways, it is an entertainers dream. Walk into a generous sized foyer that flows into a massive open concept great room featuring two entertaining areas. The Updated modern kitchen transitions easily into the dining room for connection with your guests. The new upstairs laundry room is sure to please. The master bath with en suite bathroom, 2 additional bedrooms and another full bathroom complete the main level. Downstairs you will find an additional 13x32 rec room that allows for endless possibilities. Enjoy a peaceful backyard for even more entertaining featuring an enclosed patio and outdoor firepit. Recent updates include new furnace, addition of first floor laundry room, metal roof (2022) and new turnaround in driveway (2023)
